                android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                android:layout_weight="1"
                android:textSize="20sp"
                android:textColor="@color/Black"
                android:text="The two main application areas for medically approved PVC compounds are flexible containers and tubing: containers used for blood and blood components for urine or for ostomy products and tubing used for blood taking and blood giving sets, catheters, heart-lung bypass sets, haemodialysis set etc."/>
        </TableRow>
        <TableRow
